vel\"'''<ref>{{cite news|title=\ubcfc\ube68\uac04\uc0ac\ucd98\uae30, \uc138 \ubc88\uc9f8 \ub2e8\ub3c5 \ucf58\uc11c\ud2b8 \uac1c\ucd5c\u00b7\u00b7\u00b728\uc77c \ud2f0\ucf13 \uc624\ud508|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/011/0003300247|publisher=Naver|date=2018-05-18|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| July 14, 2018\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Seoul\n| rowspan=\"2\"| South Korea\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Olympic Hall]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 6,000<ref>{{cite news|title=\ubcfc\ube68\uac04\uc0ac\ucd98\uae30, \ub2e8\ub3c5\ucf58\uc11c\ud2b8 '\uc5ec\ud589' 6\ucc9c\uc11d \ub9e4\uc9c4|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/111/0000521738|publisher=Naver|date=2018-05-29|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| July 15, 2018\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\"| '''2018 BOL4 {{small|({{lang|ja|\u8d64\u982c\u601d\u6625\u671f}})}} 1st Concert in Japan -\u65c5-'''<ref>{{cite news|title=\u8d64\u982c\u601d\u6625\u671f\u30018\u670810\u65e5\u6771\u4eac\u306b\u3066\u65e5\u672c1st\u30b3\u30f3\u30b5\u30fc\u30c8\u958b\u50ac\u6c7a\u5b9a\uff01|url=http://news.kstyle.com/m/article_amp.ksn?articleNo=2096299|publisher=Kstyle|date=2018-07-04|language=ja}}</ref>\n|-\n| August 8, 2018 {{small|(2 parts)}}\n| [[Tokyo]]\n| Japan\n| Toyosu PIT\n| 2,500<ref>{{cite news|title=\ubcfc\ube68\uac04\uc0ac\ucd98\uae30, \uccab \ubc88\uc9f8 \u65e5 \ub2e8\ub3c5 \ucf58\uc11c\ud2b8\u20262\ucc9c 5\ubc31\uc11d \uaddc\ubaa8 [\uacf5\uc2dd]|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000666331|publisher=Naver|date=2018-08-08|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" |'''Total'''\n! '''11,500'''\n|}\n\n===Headlining tours===\n* 2019 BOL4 Asia Tour \"Blossom\" (2019)\n* 2019 BOL4 Tour Concert \"Two Five\" (2019)\n* BOL4 {{small|({{lang|ja|\u8d64\u982c\u601d\u6625\u671f}})}} Live Tour 2020 \"Love\" (2020)\n\n====2019 BOL4 Asia Tour \"Blossom\"====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! width=\"200\" | Date\n! width=\"200\" | City\n! width=\"150\" | Country\n! width=\"300\" | Venue\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\"| '''2019 BOL4 Spring Solo Co