oustic version)}}\n| 117\n|}\n\n==Concert and tours==\n===Headlining concerts===\n* BOL4 1st Solo Concert \"Red Planet\" (2016)\n* BOL4 1st Concert in Taipei (2017)\n* BOL4 2nd Solo Concert \"Imagine\" (2017-2018)\n* BOL4 3rd Solo Concert \"Travel\" (2018)\n\n====BOL4 1st Solo Concert \"Red Planet\" (2016)====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! width=\"300\" | Concert\n! width=\"200\" | Date<ref>{{cite news|title=\u2018\uc74c\uc6d0 \ub300\uc138\u2019 \ubcfc\ube68\uac04\uc0ac\ucd98\uae30 \ub2e8\ub3c5 \ucf58\uc11c\ud2b8, \uc624\ud508 \ub3d9\uc2dc \ub9e4\uc9c4|url=http://m.newsen.com/news_view.php?uid=201611111447096710&r=1&http_referer=https%3A%2F%2Fm.entertain.naver.com%2Fsearch%3FsearchType%3Dissue%26searchQuery%3D%25EB%25B3%25BC%25EB%25B9%25A8%25EA%25B0%2584%25EC%2582%25AC%25EC%25B6%2598%25EA%25B8%25B0%2B%25EB%258B%25A8%25EB%258F%2585%2B%25EC%25BD%2598%25EC%2584%259C%25ED%258A%25B8%2BRED%2BPLANET%2BNO.B4120304#07pz#_enliple|publisher=Newsen|date=2016-11-11|language=ko}}</ref>\n! width=\"200\" | City\n! width=\"150\" | Country\n! width=\"300\" | Venue\n|-\n! Red Planet No. B41120\n| November 20, 2016\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[Seoul]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"| South Korea\n| Baekam Art Hall\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Red Planet No. B4120304\n| December 3, 2016\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Ewha Womans University|Ewha Womans University (Samsung Hall)]]\n|-\n| December 4, 2016\n|}\n\n====BOL4 1st Concert in Taipei (2017)====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! width=\"200\" | Date<ref>{{cite news|title=\ubcfc\ube68\uac04\uc0ac\ucd98\uae30, \uccab \ud574\uc678\ucf58\uc11c\ud2b8 \ud2f0\ucf13 2\ubd84\ub9cc\uc5d0 \ub9e4\uc9c4\u2026\uc608\ub9e4 \ucd94\uac00 \uc624\ud508|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/022/0003195628|publisher=Naver|date=2017-07-27|language=ko}}</ref>\n! width=\"200\" | City\n! width=\"150\" | Country\n! width=\"300\" | Venue\n! width=\"100\" | Attendance\n|-\n| September 9, 2017\n| [[Taipei]]\n| Taiwan\n| Legacy Taipei\n| 